        "action": "Require car and phone makers to publish annual report of safety & repair issues",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We want the Government to legally require car and phone manufacturers to report and publish all known repair and safety issues in their products, annually, broken down by model and year. We think this will help consumers make informed decisions and improve accountability across the industry.",
